text: Chiaki Tomita (born 18 October 1993) is a Japanese rower. She competed in the women's lightweight double sculls event at the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Japan Category:Rowers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:World Rowing Championships medalists for Japan
